[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Road America[/b]
Week 10 of 12 - 2017 Season 3 [/size][/color]
Race Distance: [b]10 laps[/b], approximately 25 minutes
World Record lap time: [b]2:34.651[/b] by John Ehlers (Qualifying)
(n.b. random/dynamic weather impacts lap times greatly)

Week 10 takes us to the popular Road America track. With lots of straights and overtaking opportunities this is very much a 'draft lock' track, with many races being decided by mere thousandths of a second (see the video below in the track notes for an example). Pay attention to your strategy and be patient for the right opportunity to take the win!

Target "planned" SoF race is usually 20:45 GMT Sunday, immediately following the Weekend Warriors league race.

[img]http://members.iracing.com/jforum/posts/downloadAttach/2345599.page[/img]

